  "detailed_description": "In this game, you'll play as DRUMGUY, a young man who aspires to one day become the greatest drummer to ever exist. <br>As he makes his way to the ROCKSTAR label concert, he is attacked by groups of enraged fans.<br>He'll discover soon enough that the guitarist at the head of the label is hatching a sinister plot, and will have no choice but to face this corrupt organization.<br>Express your inner drummer through battles by synchronizing each strike to the beat of the music, and fight your way to the concert to show the world what you're made of !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780/extras/f01284026a2523304b18515fa1b0618e.poster.avif?t=1744236024\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780/extras/f01284026a2523304b18515fa1b0618e.webm?t=1744236024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780/extras/f01284026a2523304b18515fa1b0618e.mp4?t=1744236024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780/extras/04d08cb4511a4bab672530dbe7725529.poster.avif?t=1744236024\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780/extras/04d08cb4511a4bab672530dbe7725529.webm?t=1744236024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780/extras/04d08cb4511a4bab672530dbe7725529.mp4?t=1744236024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046780